6:59.000Z","msg":"唔明點解仲有後生仔飲starbucks<br />\n拎住個杯以為自己好型？"},{"pid":"2d833d850ab870203874f49a1b9977a63cda97c8","tid":2141080,"uid":357892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c22197f96d39d78e7ef7f5310d688734f706c093","tid":2141080,"uid":311728,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:46:59.000Z","msg":"唔明點解仲有後生仔飲starbucks<br />\n拎住個杯以為自己好型？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"同大陸人大大個Gucci LOGO喺心口一樣"},{"pid":"965dca5d597183316609574b54d6b08c4dba994b","tid":2141080,"uid":305058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:14:09.000Z","msg":"Starfucks 同 喜茶"},{"pid":"fd99798f3b20c211cca294251ec0bfb3f4f6c586","tid":2141080,"uid":344249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"daf9fce7e27a78bdea56fdd749377475f45a419f","tid":2141080,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"825ff34a2fba193a42084ff4c91d7cbb79dbc59b","tid":2141080,"uid":78165,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"譚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:46:36.000Z","msg":"大佬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n被中資收購之謎<br />\n翻查紀錄，2017年日本丸龜製麵母公司東利多控股已收購「譚仔雲南米線」及「譚仔三哥」的全部股權。也就是說，早在黃藍之爭之前，兩個品牌就已經屬於同一集團了，而該集團並無公開其政治立場。<br />\n<br />\n不過，一波未平一波又起，又有網民發現「香港丸龜製麵」由「東利多」與一間名為「HEYI GROUP HOLDING LIMITED」的公司合作經營，前者佔37%股份，後者佔63%股份，而且是中資機構。於是又引起軒然大波，遭到網民杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n但明眼人便知，收購「譚仔」的是日本丸龜製麵母公司「東利多控股」，與大股東是中資的「香港丸龜製麵」，其實並無關係。譬如，阿媽種花，將一盆蒲公英賣了給一位鄰居，從市場上又買入兩盆蘭花，那麼兩盆蘭花與這位鄰居其實並無關係。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講就係兩間譚仔10